## Notes

- The backend project (`malayalees-us-site-boot`) may use PostgreSQL enum types with `@JdbcTypeCode(SqlTypes.OTHER)` annotation
- The batch jobs project uses VARCHAR to avoid enum type casting issues
- This pattern ensures compatibility and avoids PostgreSQL enum type casting errors
